body_html:
Hi, I bet you have installed the Tensor with the version 0.10.0rc0 (with this url $ export TF_BINARY_URL=https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/mac/cpu/tensorflow-0.11.0rc0-py2-none-any.whl); however you are running the latest version of source code 0.11.0rc0 which has conflict with the compiled tensorflow library version 0.10.0rc0.

Solution, checkout the 0.10.0rc0 version of the source code; or compile the tensorflow package again with the latest source code.

Hope this help.
